<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Important: 85% Quota Reached</title>
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #fef8f6;
        font-family: "Inter", Arial, sans-serif;
        color: #1b1b1b;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        background: #ffffff;
        margin: 40px auto;
        border-radius: 14px;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
        overflow: hidden;
        border-top: 5px solid #f77f00;
      }
      .header {
        background-color: #f77f00;
        color: #fff;
        padding: 24px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 21px;
        font-weight: 700;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 30px;
      }
      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 13px 26px;
        background-color: #d62828;
        color: #fff;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 6px;
        font-weight: 600;
        margin-top: 16px;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #777;
        padding: 22px;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        ⚠️ Usage Limit Alert — 85% Reached
      </div>

      <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{institutionName}},</p>

        <p>Your usage has now reached <strong>85%</strong> of your plan limit ({{used}} of {{limit}}).</p>

        <p>This means uploads or analytics data might soon be temporarily paused if you reach your cap.</p>

        <p>To ensure seamless athlete management and avoid disruptions, we recommend upgrading your plan today.</p>

        <a href="{{upgradeLink}}" class="cta-button">Upgrade My Plan</a>

        <p style="margin-top: 28px;">You’re doing great — keep your institution running without interruptions.</p>

        <p>— Project Athlete 360 Team</p>
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        This alert was automatically sent when your account exceeded 85% usage.<br />
        © {{year}} Project Athlete 360 — All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>